{{ block content }}

    <p>
        <ul>
            <li>There will be 10 rounds, and in all rounds you will begin with a new endowment of 20 tokens, each of which can either be kept or contributed to the project. The 3 other players in your group will also have 20 tokens.</li>
            <li>Everybody earns money in the same manner: 1 token for each token kept, 0.4 tokens for each token contributed, and 0.4 tokens for each token contributed by the 3 other players.</li>
            <li>At the start of a new round, you will be given a new endowment of 20 tokens. You are free to change the numbers of tokens kept and contributed from round to round.</li>
            <li>Note: You will be matched with the same players in all rounds.</li>
    </p>



